<th valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Specificity</th>
<th valign="top" align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Mean AUC (Repeated 10-fold with 30 cycles)</th>
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
